    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIR\nCALIFORNIA\nTIMETABLE\nEffective September 5, 1979\nAir California\nONTARIO-SAN FRANCISCO\nNEW NONSTOP SERVICE\nSERVING CALIFORNIA AND NEVADA",
      "AR\nCALIFORNIA\nOPENS ITS NEWEST\nAIRPORT FACILITY.\nAir California\nOn September 5th, Air California opened its new facilities at San Francisco International's north terminal.\nNow, taking off on Air California is easier than ever. You'll walk less. Get to your flight sooner.\nBe closer to all services. Including easy check-in counters, nearby parking, and curbside access to\nbaggage claim areas.\nYou'll also find a complete array of travel services. Everything from rental car agencies,\nnari\nclose-by hotel/motel phones, magazines and sundries, to your choice of seven\nDaciol\nrestaurants. Plus cocktail lounges, an espresso cafe, shops, a bank, a spacious, fully\nstaffed nursery and abundant public seating areas.\nAnd our new close-in gates will lead you to flights throughout California\nand Nevada. Or bring you to connecting flights serving the United States.\nCALIFORNIA\nWe make it easy to fly."
    ],
